Package: rnaseqtools
Type: Package
Title: Helpers for dealing with our RNA-seq output
Version: 0.0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Richard", "White", email = "rich@bushclab.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of helper functions for dealing with RNA-seq output files.
    Includes functions for loading output files from DESeq2, 
    dealing with differences in column names, getting normalised counts etc.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    DESeq2,
    readr,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    rlang
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
